features: 【𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐧 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐭𝐲𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐡 𝐄𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞】This end table is designed with a C shape and features a rattan storge shelf. The rattan storge shelf was used for newspapers and magazines, combines modern and Bohemian element to make the room more stylish and practical.

【𝐒𝐢𝐝𝐞 𝐭𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐠𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧】The small side table is embedded with 2 standard power outlets, 2 USB ports, which help you charge phone, tablet, smart watch and other electronics conveniently. The position of the charging station is safe and space saving.

【𝐕𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐄𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞】The slim c table with 4 removable wheels can slide under a sofa, couch or bed, allowing you to read books, have coffee, enjoy snacks while sitting on sofa; works great as an end table, laptop table, bedside table and coffee table.

【𝐃𝐮𝐫𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐝𝐲】TRIFEBLE end table is made of waterproof particleboard, c shape sturdy steel frame and corrosion-resistant PVC rattan. In addition, we provide two lockable wheels, you can fix the wheels at any time to ensure the stability of the table.

【𝐄𝐚𝐬𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐥𝐞】Simple product construction, numbered parts and detailed instructions allow you to effortlessly assemble this nesting end table set quickly with tools in the package. Any questions of the installation have, please contact us freely.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: My fiance is always on his computer because He makes music and he likes surfing the web for new instrumentals he always Stacks pillows up on his lap and put his computer on top so I figured this would be a nice little gift for him so he can have a little desk that he can work on instead of using his pillows first things first it was easy to assemble it only took 15 minutes all the required piece were in the box I learned that after we put this beautiful End Table with Charging Station together we could not slide it under the bed and where it was able to be used this is for a bed that is low ground you cannot use this if you have a high bed because it does not adjust that will be a really great feature to have on this end table work desk that way if you have a high bed you can adjust it up and if you have a low bed you can adjust it down the fact that this does not work for using with our king size bed we now have to put it in a guest room because it can be used with our queen size bed or we can push it on wheels to the living room and use with our recliner however everything else worked great I plugged in my phone until the USB port and my phone charged within 30 minutes I plugged in a lamp and it came on so the electrical charging port works very well pushing this around on Wheels also was a breeze the wheels did not get stuck nor scratch my hardware floors I enjoy the soft top wood desk part of this end table it is very smooth the legs are made of steel and so is the book holder part I highly recommend this for someone in college or just to have around the house but with a lower bed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fast charging plug and nice space saver table!
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for using in smaller spaces like apartments or RV's, and the plug that is on it charges your devices super fast, which was a pleasant surprise for me I know. My laptop fits perfectly on top of the table and it will roll underneath the chair I sit on while using it, putting it at exactly the height I need it to be at so I can use my computer comfortably as well as write or any other tasks that require a small table top to do. It is also a sleek design and looks nice with all of the other stuff in the room, very simple looking yet sleek and elegant as well. Assembly was rather straightforward and for the most part simple enough, I was able to figure out what wasn't clear in the instructions provided. Also included extra hardware and the tools needed to put it together.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is actually very easy to put together! Hubby did it in 15-20 mins! Came with all screws and accessories you need! Love it! We use it daily! Quality much better than expected! Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: This is one of the easiest tables I've assembled in a long time. It looks good and the wheels make it really versatile. It can be moved to any room you need it in. It can also be used up against a sofa or chair. It's sturdy and holds a good deal. The charging station is a bonus and works well. It also doesn't take up any of the table top space since it's placed on the side/front of the table. Good price point at under 40.00.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact Sturdy Portable Laptop Computer Desk
reviews.reviewText: I use this as a compact portable laptop computer desk. It's small size and built in AC & USB receptacles are a perfect fit for small spaces. Assembly took about 30 minutes and it came with all the necessary tools.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent small side table for sofa
reviews.reviewText: I thought this small table on casters is perfect for sliding under the sofa for watching TV while eating, snacking, or playing with tablet. The assembly took about 20 minutes. The materials is thin and on the cheap side, but it serves its purpose as a lightweight table and the price is good.
